com.appiancorp.suiteapi.process

Class ProcessModelSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appiancorp.suiteapi.common.Identity
      • com.appiancorp.suiteapi.process.ProcessModelProperties
        • com.appiancorp.suiteapi.process.ProcessModelSummary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LocalId, XMLable, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProcessModelDetails

    public class ProcessModelSummary
extends ProcessModelProperties
implements XMLable
    Holds summary information about a process model, such as who created it, when, how many process instances are running, and how many have completed.
